verses:
Praise the Lord in heaven
Praise Him in His holy place
Praise for His greatness
Praise for His powerful deeds

Praise the lord with trumpets
Praise with a thousand strings
Praise the Lord with dancing
Praise Him with joyful sounds

Praise the Lord with cymbal
Praise Him with resounding brass
Praise Him all living
Praise the Lord forever more

Praise the Glorious Father
Praise the Everlasting Son
Praise the Holy Spirit
Praise the glory, three in one
